NExtJs with Shandcn
----------------------

npx create-next-app@latest . which indicates the folder name to be the current project name
Eslint-->suggestive errors we get
suggestion add src directory-(yes) also APP router(yes)
Uses @ instead of ../../ (@ indicates root directory)

src-->app->page.tsx acts like app.js

/chai
app->chai->page.tsx

REMEMBER-->api folder name to not give as it for backend

npx shadcn-ui@0.7.0
use typescript-->base color(slate)-->src/app/global.css--->tailwind.config.ts

now go to documantation and to add button paste npx ...... add button (it adds the button.tsx to the componenets->ui)

how to use
------------
import Button from /components/ui/button
<Button>Shadcn button</Button>
